  • Automela
    • Mode 1
      • As a citizen of the desert
          Τῆς ἐρήμου πολίτης
        • Score: Staff
      • For all the powers of heaven (aka For the celestial orders)
          Τῶν οὐρανίων ταγμάτων
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
        • Audio
      • In heaven be amazed
          Χορὸς ἀγγελικός
        • Score: Staff
      • O Martyrs extolled
          Πανεύφημοι μάρτυρες
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
        • Audio
      • The soldiers who were guarding (soft chromatic)
          Τὸν τάφον σου Σωτήρ
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
        • Audio
      • The soldiers who were guarding (diatonic)
          Τὸν τάφον σου Σωτήρ. Diatonic version is used for apolytikia.
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
      • The stone having been sealed
          Τοῦ λίθου σφραγισθέντος
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
        • Audio
      • Marvel at the wondrous paradox (aka What a paradoxal miracle)
          Ὢ τοῦ παραδόξου θαύµατος
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
      • When You come down
          Ὅταν ἔλθῃς ὁ Θεός
        • Score: Staff
    • Mode 2
      • Are there any worthy crowns (AKA Which are the wreaths)
          Ποίοις εὐφημιῶν στέμμασιν
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
        • Audio
      • As the Mother of God
          Εὐσπλαγχνίας ὑπάρχουσα
        • Score: Staff

          Τὰ ἄνω ζητῶν
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
        • Audio

          Ὅτε ἐκ τοῦ ξύλου
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
        • Audio

          Οἶκος τοῦ Ἐφραθᾶ
        • Score: Byzantine
        • Score: Staff
        • Audio
